                "value": 0.86
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Measurements we made with both",
                "enriched and natural targets. One 46Ti target",
                "enriched to 86% abundance was made by evaporation.",
                "The thickness of this target was also determined by",
                "comparing its yield to that of the natural abundance",
                "targets but at an incident lab energy of 1.22 MeV.",
                "Titanium targets of naturally occurring abundances",
                "were prepared by evaporation onto 0.5 mm tantalum",
                "pieces. Titanium targets were ~400 microg/cm2 thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
