              "free_text": [
                " Measurements we made with both",
                "enriched and natural targets. Four 50Cr targets",
                "enriched to 98.6%, with thicknesses of approximately",
                "520, 580, 600 and 750 microg/cm2 were made by",
                "evaporation. The enriched 50Cr target thicknesses",
                "were determined by comparing the yield from the",
                "enriched targets to the yield of the natural",
                "abundance targets at an incident lab energy of 1.40",
                "MeV. Chromium targets of naturally occurring",
                "abundances were prepared by evaporation onto 0.5 mm",
                "tantalum pieces. The chromium targets were ~600",
                "microg/cm2 thick."
              ]
            }
